text: "Enemies" is a 2019 song by Post Malone featuring DaBaby. It was taken from his third studio album Hollywood's Bleeding. It went to number 16 in the United States and Hungary, number 15 in Canada, number 37 in New Zealand, number 17 in Norway, number 28 in Lithuania and Australia and number 25 in Denmark. ==References== Category:2019 songs Category:Post Malone songs Category:DaBaby songs
title: Enemies (Post Malone song)
